5014 - Tyres and Tubes Summary > HANKOOKTYRE AUSTRALIA RETAIL PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover tyres and tubes. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. HANKOOKTYRE AUSTRALIA RETAIL PTY LTD is headquartered in Crows Nest, New South Wales. It is headed by director & company secretary Junghee Cho. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $30.48 million. Its net profit totalled $2.25 million. HANKOOKTYRE AUSTRALIA RETAIL PTY LTD forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
